{
  "id": "L17",
  "title": "Talking About Your Work or Studies",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Welcome! In this lesson, you'll learn how to talk about your job or studies. A common question at a party is 'Che lavoro fai?' (What do you do for work?). Let's learn how to answer."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L17_E01",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Che lavoro fai?",
        "meaning": "What do you do for work?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L17_E02",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Faccio il...",
        "meaning": "I am a... (for a masculine profession)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L17_E03",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Faccio la...",
        "meaning": "I am a... (for a feminine profession)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L17_V01",
      "data": {
        "Il programmatore": "The programmer"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L17_V02",
      "data": {
        "La dottoressa": "The doctor (female)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L17_E04",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Studio...",
        "meaning": "I study..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L17_V03",
      "data": {
        "Storia": "History"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L17_E05",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Lavoro per...",
        "meaning": "I work for..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L17_V04",
      "data": {
        "Un'azienda": "A company"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L17_E06",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Ti piace?",
        "meaning": "Do you like it?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L17_E07",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Mi piace molto",
        "meaning": "I like it a lot"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L17_S01",
      "title": "Stating Your Profession",
      "setting": "You're at a party and meet Giulia. She asks what you do.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Answer Giulia's question",
          "chatbot_message": "Ciao! Piacere di conoscerti. Che lavoro fai?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Mention your company or university",
          "chatbot_message": "Interessante! E dove lavori o studi?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Say if you like your job or studies",
          "chatbot_message": "Ah, capisco. E ti piace?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Great! Now let's add more detail, like your specific tasks and how long you've been working or studying."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L17_E08",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Cosa fai esattamente?",
        "meaning": "What do you do exactly?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L17_E09",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Scrivo email",
        "meaning": "I write emails"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L17_E10",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Leggo libri",
        "meaning": "I read books"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L17_V05",
      "data": {
        "A tempo pieno": "Full-time"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L17_V06",
      "data": {
        "Part-time": "Part-time"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L17_E11",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Da quanto tempo?",
        "meaning": "For how long?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L17_V07",
      "data": {
        "Da": "For / Since (referring to time)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L17_V08",
      "data": {
        "Due anni": "Two years"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L17_S02",
      "title": "Describing Your Responsibilities",
      "setting": "The conversation with Giulia continues. She's curious for more details.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Describe a main task you do",
          "chatbot_message": "Bene! E cosa fai esattamente?"
        },
        {
          "title": "State if it's full-time or part-time",
          "chatbot_message": "Capisco. È a tempo pieno?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Say how long you have been doing it",
          "chatbot_message": "Ok. E da quanto tempo lo fai?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Excellent work. Now it's your turn to ask Giulia about her job. Let's learn how."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L17_E12",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "E tu?",
        "meaning": "And you?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L17_V09",
      "data": {
        "L'insegnante": "The teacher"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L17_V10",
      "data": {
        "La scuola": "The school"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L17_E13",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Hai dei colleghi simpatici?",
        "meaning": "Do you have nice colleagues?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L17_V11",
      "data": {
        "I colleghi": "The colleagues"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L17_P01",
      "data": {
        "word": "colleghi",
        "phonetic": "/kolˈlɛ.ɡi/",
        "tip": "The 'gh' sound in Italian is a hard 'g', like in the English word 'go'. It's never silent."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L17_E14",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Sembra interessante",
        "meaning": "That sounds interesting"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L17_E15",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Che bello!",
        "meaning": "How nice!"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L17_S03",
      "title": "Asking About Their Job",
      "setting": "Now it's your turn to guide the conversation with Giulia.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Ask what she does for work",
          "chatbot_message": "Wow, capisco."
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask if she has nice colleagues",
          "chatbot_message": "Io faccio l'insegnante. Lavoro in una scuola."
        },
        {
          "title": "Make a positive comment about her job",
          "chatbot_message": "Sì, i miei colleghi sono molto simpatici. Mi piace il mio lavoro."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}